channel.title: Hey everyone - I am on old member that has matured
channel.description:
Hey everyone. Some of you might know me and some of you might not. I am [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=127502]CopyRight[/url]. For you that don't know me I am an old member that was very immature back in the day. I got into some bad situations that have gotten me banned, even permanent banned. I am 15 right now, almost 16. I really want to get back into this community again, it was a great community to be apart of.
Do you, including the staff, think it is possible for me to come back.
Please don't post anything that is disrespectful. I actually want to come back.
